    <item>
      <title>韩国的婚姻跳跃，为衰老国家提供了希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/south-korea-s-marriages-jump-offering-hopes-for-aging-nation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国婚姻在一个充满希望的迹象中提高了韩国婚姻，这是一个充满希望的迹象，而这个国家一直在加大努力，以提高世界上最低的生育率，这是经济上悲观情绪的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/south-korea-s-marriages-jump-offering-hopes-for-aging-nation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，美联储应降低费率，因为关税会加热</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/trump-says-fed-should-cut-rates-as-tariff-push-heats-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，美联储应降低利率，并随着官员的关税推动而权衡的经济成本而与美国中央银行分裂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/trump-says-fed-should-cut-rates-as-tariff-push-heats-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 02:20:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚的达顿说，如果当选，特朗普会议将首先</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/australia-s-dutton-says-trump-meeting-will-be-first-if-elected</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚的反对派领导人表示，如果他赢得即将举行的选举，他将首次对美国与唐纳德·特朗普会面，以与新政府的紧张局势消除，但长期以来，盟友必须加深他们的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/australia-s-dutton-says-trump-meeting-will-be-first-if-elected</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 02:19:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>弗雷迪·麦克（Freddie Mac）告诉工人全职返回办公室</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/fhfa-director-calls-freddie-mac-workers-back-to-office-full-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[弗雷迪·麦克（Freddie Mac）告诉员工，他们将每周从5月开始五天从办公室工作，并承诺审查薪酬计划，以奖励关键人物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/fhfa-director-calls-freddie-mac-workers-back-to-office-full-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 00:42:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>多年的煤炭反弹破坏了印度的能源安全推动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/years-of-coal-backlash-undermine-india-s-energy-security-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了满足其不断增长的能源需求，印度扩大世界上最大的煤炭动力舰队之一的计划是由于能够和愿意帮助建造新工厂的公司而撤销的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/years-of-coal-backlash-undermine-india-s-energy-security-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 00:21:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普着手签署行政命令拆除教育部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-set-to-sign-executive-order-eliminating-education-department</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）有望签署一项行政诉讼，要求官员采取措施拆除教育部，这是他为减少联邦政府及其劳动力规模的最新努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-set-to-sign-executive-order-eliminating-education-department</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 22:48:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
